            </stepxmp>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">To obtain the license, copy the environment code from the
license requested window by clicking <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Copy</uicontrol> and
send this code to your licensing server or your local Schneider Electric
contact. See Service View for more information.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">When you receive your license code, paste it into the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Your license</uicontrol> field and click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Valid</uicontrol>. This license is valid for a year.</cmd>
